Goodwin Says ECB Should Learn From Swiss National Bank

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-30T17:07:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/goodwin-says-ecb-should-learn-from-swiss-national-bank-video-.html
Fred Goodwin , a cross-asset 
strategist at State Street Bank & Trust Co., talks about the 
European sovereign-debt crisis, its impact on European equities 
and banks, and the  Swiss National Bank 's efforts to defend the 
cap on the franc.  Goodwin, speaking with  Tom Keene  on Bloomberg Television's 
"Surveillance Midday," also discusses the options markets. 
(Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:34
 